------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
|Communications, Public Works, and Tra-|648,826,158                           | 
|nsportation                           |                                      | 
------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
|Natural Resources                     |203,511,260                           | 
------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
|Planning and Budget                   |17,481,499                            | 
------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
|Public Debt                           |2,115,317,279                         | 
------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
|Executive Branch Centralized Public S-|653,062,690                           | 
|pending Services                      |                                      | 
------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
|Secretariat of the Environment        |2,371,185                             | 
------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 


  The National Congress is supposed to approve the national 
budget today, since the closing ceremonies for the fourth 
session of the current constitutional term are scheduled to be 
held tomorrow, Friday, at 1000 

</TEXT>

