Language: <F P=105> Spanish </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Excerpt] Carabineros Director General Rodolfo Stange has 
rejected the allegations of an international report in which 
Chile is listed as one of the countries where human rights are 
still being violated. Stange refused to comment at length on a 
recent report on this subject. 
