Furthermore, the foreign minister said yesterday that he was 
studying and assessing the report in order to make a decision. 
Therefore, since the Foreign Ministry is already taking care of 
the matter, anything I could say would be out of place. 
  [Question indistinct] 
  [Stange] In any case I reject these...these groundless 
charges from a foreign country which does not [changes 
thought]...which has, let us say, other problems to deal with. 
[end recording] [passage omitted] 

