<F P=106> [From the "NTC" newscast] </F>
  [Text] Ernesto Samper, the Liberal Party presidential 
hopeful with the best chances of winning the election, is ready 
to fight against the presence of U.S. soldiers in Juan Chaco. 
  When referring to the presence of U.S. troops in Juan Chaco, 
Ernesto Samper Pizano said President Cesar Gaviria allowed the 
