twice as much unemployment as the rest of the country. What we 
need are public works projects that put our own people to work. 
I believe the U.S. Government or the Defense Ministry has 
pulled a fast one on President Gaviria. [end recording] 
  Samper also said there is a need to integrate the Pacific 
region into the nation's development plans. 

