<H3> <TI>   * Drug Money Alleged in Congressional Campaigns </TI></H3>
<H4>   * Senator Says Allegations `True' </H4>
<F P=102> 94P20340D Santa Fe de Bogota EL ESPECTADOR in Spanish 10 Jan 
p 5A </F>

