investment, especially in the tourism sector. Businessmen who 
invest on the island, he pointed out, will recover their 
investments quickly. 
  Lage and accompanying delegation will travel to Rio de 
Janeiro early tomorrow morning, where they will meet with local 
businessmen and political personalities. 

